He had the impression that Mr. El Ibrashi and Mr. Gil Lavedra would have liked the text to be completely redrafted , but Mr. Gil Lavedra had now said that if paragraph 2 ( b ) could be shortened , he could accept the remainder .
If Mr. El Ibrashi agreed to that proposal , the Committee &apos;s representative in the Preparatory Committee could be requested at the next session to present the points in greater detail when the Preparatory Committee met in April 1993 .
