26 . Mr. MIKHAILOV said that , when proposing the establishment of the working group that had prepared the original text , he had intended that it should concentrate on questions that were specific to the Committee rather than on general questions , but too much time had been spent in discussing the title and there had been no opportunity to consider the substantive questions .
