30 . Mr. BURNS said that the revised text was entitled : &quot; Recommendations by the Committee Against Torture to the Preparatory Committee of the World Conference as well as to the Conference itself &quot; and read :
1 . Appoints Mr. Sorensen as representative and Mr. Mikhailov as alternate to the meetings of the Preparatory Committee of the World Conference on Human Rights ,
( a ) With a view to eradicating torture by the year 2000 , that subject matter should be included in the agenda of the World Conference .
